  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this randomized controlled trial is to examine the impact of a patient
      decision aid on the quality of decisions about managing symptoms of depression. In
      particular, we will examine whether the decision aid increases knowledge about
      depression/managing depression symptoms and concordance between goals and treatment choices.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
